Select the project Right click and Add / New item / User Interface /form and name it as required.( The name of both Table and Form should be same )
Drag the table from the project on to the data source node in the form designer.
change the properties to NO (Allow Create , Allow Delete ,Insert at End,Insert If Empty)
The Form Desinger is broken into Three parts as 
>> Form Pane
>> Design Pane
>> Preview Pane
The Properties to be modified 
>> caption
>> Data Source
>> Title Data Source
Right Click On Design Node / Apply Pattern / Table of Contents
Right Click on the Design Node and Choose New / Tab.
The error gets corrected . Rename the new control to Parameter Tab Page.
The first Tab is Usally a General settings so name the tab as General TabPage.And Find a Suitable Label For that and enter in a caption property.
we need to add two Group Controls.
Right click on the General Tab Page  New / Group 
Rename the new Group Control General Title Group.




